</span></span></span><![endif]>Binding Model</a></h2>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>Field controls bind to a field on an entity.</p>

<h3 style=3D'mso-list:l90 level3 lfo137'><![if !supportLists]><span
style=3D'mso-fareast-font-family:Aptos;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;
