style=3D'mso-list:Ignore'>6.2.1<span style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'=
>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><![endif]>Binding Object</h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>{<br>
<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>&quot;entity&quot;: &quot;<span
class=3DSpellE>entityNameOrId</span>&quot;,<br>
<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>&quot;field&quot;: &quot;<span
class=3DSpellE>fieldNameOrId</span>&quot;<br>
}</p>

