<p class=3DMsoNormal>Each field control type may define additional configur=
ation
fields.</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>These are stored under <span class=3DSpellE>editorConf=
ig</span>.</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>Examples</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>Textbox</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>&quot;<span class=3DSpellE>editorConfig</span>&quot;: =
{<br>
<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>&quot;<span class=3DSpellE>maxLen=
gth</span>&quot;:
255,<br>
<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>&quot;placeholder&quot;: &quot;En=
ter
text...&quot;<br>
}</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>Number</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>&quot;<span class=3DSpellE>editorConfig</span>&quot;: =
{<br>
<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>&quot;min&quot;: 0,<br>
<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>&quot;max&quot;: 100,<br>
<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>&quot;precision&quot;: 2<br>
}</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>Dropdown</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>&quot;<span class=3DSpellE>editorConfig</span>&quot;: =
{<br>
<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>&quot;<span class=3DSpellE>listTy=
pe</span>&quot;:
&quot;countries&quot;,<br>
<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>&quot;<span class=3DSpellE>allowC=
ustom</span>&quot;:
false<br>
}</p>

